                    <characteristic name="Summary" typeId="fdcc-276a-cadb-7810"/>
                    <characteristic name="Description" typeId="516b-bc6f-e52f-aced">A Model with a Wings has their Movement Characteristic set to 12. Each time a Dangerous Terrain test is made for a Model with wings, that Test is automatically passed.</characteristic>
