          </infoLinks>
          <rules>
            <rule name="Floating Bomb" id="7be8-8fe1-527d-f06d" hidden="false">
              <description>f a Charge Roll made for a Model with this Special Rule is failed, the Model is Removed as a Casualty, but immediately explodes as described in the Explodes (X) Special Rule. If a Charge Roll made for a Model with this Special Rule is successful, then at the end of Step 2 of the Fight Sub-Phase of that Combat, every Unit in that Combat suffers a number of automatic Hits equal to the total number of Wounds among all Models in the Unit which Charged. Each such Hit has a Strength of 8, an AP of 4 and a Damage of 2. Once these Hits have been fully resolved, the Model with this Special Rule is immediately Removed as a Casualty, and any version of the Explodes (X) Special Rule it has is ignored.</description>
            </rule>
          </rules>
          <constraints>
            <constraint type="min" value="3" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="true" id="980f-90de-58be-6811" includeChildSelections="false"/>
            <constraint type="max" value="9" field="selections" scope="parent" shared="true" id="d38b-5583-3499-a848" includeChildSelections="false"/>
